Dialogue: 0,0:00:-12.-27,0:00:-10.-26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-10.-24,0:00:-08.-36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger,\Nthe King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-08.-34,0:00:-06.-05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-03,0:00:-02.-18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before\Nhis death drove people to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-16,0:00:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure?\NIf you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.67,0:00:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.85,0:00:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men head for the Grand Line\Nin pursuit of their dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.59,0:00:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered\Na Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.86,0:00:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE PIECE!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compasses only cause delays
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.61,0:00:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delirious with fever,\NI take the helm
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the dusty treasure map has\Nbeen verified, it's not a legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.46,0:01:03.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to personal storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,simply ride aboard\Nsomeone else's biorhythm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.47,0:01:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and pretend it isn't there!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.14,0:01:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to gather up\Nall our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set out in search\Nof something to find
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.36,0:01:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A coin in my pocket,\Nand do you wanna be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.60,0:01:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are, We are on the cruise!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What great weather!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.11,0:01:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep going this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.44,0:01:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we should see the\Nnavy base island soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.25,0:01:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Coby! You're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.88,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're actually gonna\Nreach our destination?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.55,0:01:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.72,0:01:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the bare\Nminimum skills all sailors need!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.42,0:01:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time\Nto be laughing, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.56,0:02:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being held prisoner there.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The famous pirate hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.16,0:02:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.70,0:02:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's chopped up\Nbounties like a bloodthirsty beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.98,0:02:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People say he's a\Ndemon in human form!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.65,0:02:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Enter the Great Swordsman!\NPirate Hunter Roronoa Zoro"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it! The navy base city!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:49.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're crazy to want him to join you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.21,0:02:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't decided yet.\NI just wanna see if he's a good guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.14,0:02:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's been caught\Nbecause he's a bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mm! Yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know if Zoro's at the base?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem the name "Zoro" is taboo here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.86,0:03:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's check out the base anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna be a marine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes... But I'm not really ready yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rumor has it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.97,0:03:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a guy named\NCaptain Morgan is at this base, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a funny town!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:32.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.95,0:03:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand Zoro, but why are\Nthey afraid of a navy captain's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly feel uneasy about this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.46,0:03:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure they didn't jump just for fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.90,0:03:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.43,0:03:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! This's the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm finally here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this is where\Nwe part ways, Luffy-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only for a short time, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.91,0:03:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upsy-daisy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.41,0:04:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! What in the world are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.55,0:04:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where's this demon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.25,0:04:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.42,0:04:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's in\Na prison cell or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.52,0:04:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.52,0:04:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See! There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!\NHe wouldn't be out--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.57,0:04:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A black hood and a haramaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Roronoa Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.11,0:04:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can get away easy\Nif we untie those ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't be stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.85,0:04:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no telling what'll\Nhappen if we let him loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he'd try to kill you too, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.82,0:04:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.92,0:04:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.13,0:05:02.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! There's no way you\Ncould survive with him on your crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Stop her, Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.89,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be hungry!\NI made you some rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:21.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna get killed, pipsqueak? Scram!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't eaten anything this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:27.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! This is my first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.77,0:05:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I worked really hard to make them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.37,0:05:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eyesore!\NGet the hell outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want 'em!\NDon't make me kick your ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.84,0:05:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not nice to be a bully!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You seem surprisingly well, Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.12,0:05:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now there's another weird guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must be with the navy!\NNow that girl will be safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.39,0:05:58.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Those are some\Ntasty-looking rice balls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:02.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too damn sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those're full of sugar!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:07.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to use salt for rice balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:11.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I thought they\Nmight taste better sweet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Take this! And this!\N--Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-How horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.29,0:06:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I worked so hard to make those...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.43,0:06:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not read this notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.23,0:06:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Those who help\Ncriminals will be executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:38.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Navy Captain Morgan"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.10,0:06:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like even little brats\Nknow how scary my dad is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then that's Captain Morgan's son?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.91,0:06:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You. Throw this kid out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.95,0:06:52.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said throw her over the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.65,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or can you not follow my orders?!\NDon't make me tell my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.39,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.39,0:07:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, little girl.\NCurl yourself into a ball.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.21,0:07:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Luffy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.61,0:07:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.44,0:07:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe how\Nhorrible that guy is!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.78,0:07:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.98,0:07:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are stubborn about staying alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.86,0:07:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I will live the full month!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good luck with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten days left, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Assuming you can live that long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can he be so cruel, Luffy-san?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you're a bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.25,0:08:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being stuck out here for all to see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really strong at all?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.96,0:08:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it were me, I'd probably\Nstarve to death in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.80,0:08:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got more spirit than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.23,0:08:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.30,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.20,0:08:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a strange person!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.54,0:08:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.84,0:08:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you pick that up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.41,0:08:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's mostly a mud ball now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and give it here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Told you so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.89,0:08:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.59,0:08:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.26,0:08:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.27,0:08:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He ate every last bite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.21,0:08:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Zoro really as evil\Nas the rumors say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.94,0:08:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.61,0:09:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, he let himself\Nget crucified in our place...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.38,0:09:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.85,0:09:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all that Helmeppo's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.72,0:09:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's Captain Morgan's son...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make way for my adorable pet-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the way, and you get executed!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.64,0:09:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gonna complain about\Nwhat my pet-sama's doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rika! Stop that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get in trouble\Nif we go against him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, crap!\N--He's in trouble now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.76,0:09:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.77,0:09:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...pirate hunter Zoro?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.77,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.64,0:10:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a pirate hunter defying the navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and let me eat in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're annoying me.\NBoth you and your pet-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.33,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do realize that if my\Ndad finds out about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're gonna get\Nexecuted for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say? Let's make a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You get strung up in place\Nof this mother and daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For, yeah, one month...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can survive for one month,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.15,0:10:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you live, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whadya say?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.79,0:10:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One month.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been three weeks since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:07.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo punches and\Nkicks him while he's tied up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.51,0:11:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.04,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!\NLet us all eat for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.02,0:11:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Bring me some booze!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.29,0:11:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit dawdling! Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.73,0:11:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.26,0:11:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been bored lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.93,0:11:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I've decided\Nto execute Zoro tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.43,0:11:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.78,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy is scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Captain Morgan's son, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.52,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:11:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna tell my dad\Nand he's gonna execute you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.92,0:12:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight me yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get\Non the navy's bad side?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've made up my mind, Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.63,0:12:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... going to have Zoro join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.94,0:12:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.18,0:12:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,great!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.54,0:12:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You're exactly right,\NCaptain Morgan, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.45,0:12:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hasn't tribute to me\Nbeen a bit lacking lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.69,0:12:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, the citizens'\Nwallets do have their limits...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.19,0:12:35.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The issue is the level of respect for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.33,0:12:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.33,0:12:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I want you to slaughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:25.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to die\Nin a place like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.69,0:13:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again?\NYou sure have lots of free time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll untie you, so join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.36,0:13:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.40,0:13:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for people\Nto join my pirate crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it!\NMe, stooping to a criminal's level?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.27,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with being a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates are despicable!\NAs if I'd wanna be one!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.31,0:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already known\Nas an evil bounty hunter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People can say whatever they want,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.55,0:14:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I ain't done anything I regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.19,0:14:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will live through this\Nand accomplish what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.76,0:14:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I've decided you're gonna join me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit deciding on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.90,0:14:25.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear you use swords.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But that stupid son took my stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:32.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go get it back for you!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if you want your sword, join my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.38,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really getting on my nerves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he planning to bust\Ninto the base by himself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.45,0:14:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! The base is\Nin the other direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell is that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Stop there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand it up in one shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! Why aren't you\Ngoing to get revenge?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.28,0:15:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even you've ever hit me in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.99,0:15:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why I've never hit you before?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.56,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Because you think I'm--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.80,0:15:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Because you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a stupid son who\Nisn't even worth hitting!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.48,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad is the one who's great! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.96,0:16:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which reminds me, I hear a rat\Nsnuck into the crucifixion yard.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.77,0:16:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-If you mean that pipsqueak,\NI made sure she was dealt with--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You killed her, I hope?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! I mean, she was just a little kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.21,0:16:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.88,0:16:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go into town and exterminate her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't be serious!\NShe's just a little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't in good conscience...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.98,0:16:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who disobeys my\Norders is a traitor, even little brats.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But... I can't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.26,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.66,0:16:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You didn't have to go that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.17,0:16:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was with my strength that\NI rose to my rank of captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.97,0:16:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! In this world,\Ntitles mean everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.24,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that I, the captain and\Nhighest ranking officer at this base,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,am the most superior person here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.78,0:16:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So everything I do is right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.29,0:16:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right, you guys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!\NYou're absolutely correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.43,0:17:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid's death can wait for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.20,0:17:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Observe! This is the symbol of my authority,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.13,0:17:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which took many years to finally complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, stand it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Display my greatness\Nat the top of this base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.85,0:17:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's weird.\NThere's no one here...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta find that stupid son\Nand get Zoro's sword back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull! Pull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bumped it, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.30,0:17:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard something up there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.74,0:17:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry, sir! I was careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:53.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to think\Nof this statue as me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The slightest scratch or speck\Nof dirt is treachery against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I jumped too far!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.96,0:18:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What is that?!\N--It flew up from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.08,0:18:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seize him!\NI'm going to kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad! That's him!\NHe's the guy who hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.95,0:18:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been looking for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.62,0:18:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me!\NThere's something I want you to give back!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.83,0:18:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Let me go!\N--Helmeppo-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.43,0:18:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him! Don't let him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.73,0:18:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! There's someone\Nin the crucifixion yard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one traitor after the other...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After him! After him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone just had to interrupt...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.22,0:19:15.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Zoro's sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you! I'll tell you!\NJust stop dragging me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.13,0:19:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.43,0:19:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my room...\NWe just passed it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why didn't you say so?\NNow we gotta go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Freeze!\N--Let Helmeppo-sama go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead and shoot, if you dare!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.71,0:19:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.82,0:19:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please escape, Zoro-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.99,0:19:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be killed for doing that, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.59,0:19:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand to watch\Nthe navy like this anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to be\Nan honorable marine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! I can't escape!\NI only got ten days until--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.23,0:19:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to be\Nexecuted tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:19:58.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.87,0:20:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmeppo never once\Nintended to honor your agreement!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Luffy-san got angry and punched him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.28,0:20:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The navy is after Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't ask you to be a pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please, help Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.26,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san is the only\None who can save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I think you're also the only\None who can save Luffy-san now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the crime of treachery against me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.35,0:20:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll now execute you two where you stand!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.42,0:20:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This the room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.33,0:20:58.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there are three here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.56,0:21:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Which sword is Zoro's?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.13,0:21:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coby!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is some interesting\Nstuff you guys've pulled!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.95,0:21:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you two and that straw hat\Nkid plannin' a coup or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always fought alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.19,0:21:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike arrogant bastards like\Nyou who use soldiers as cronies!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roronoa Zoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.73,0:21:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.50,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may be strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.00,0:21:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but before my authority,\Nyou're as good as scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aim!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.97,0:21:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.28,0:21:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can't afford to die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.98,0:21:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still as weak as ever, Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.26,0:21:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.73,0:22:05.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What are you--?!\N--Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.30,0:22:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.74,0:22:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't work!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.21,0:22:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I was strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.91,0:22:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Monkey D. Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.52,0:22:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The man who's gonna\Nbe King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To be continued"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was little, I had\Na vision of a treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.28,0:23:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I always searched\Nfor that miraculous place
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before someone else could\Nbeat me to it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.93,0:23:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the world is going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.41,0:23:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before I can even attain my dream
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.41,0:23:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then take me to the time\Nwhen I knew nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.49,0:23:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that my memories won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the world's greatest swordsman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.81,0:24:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Why not be a great swordsman pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.14,0:24:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk like it's so easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.45,0:24:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The soldiers have started to go berserk!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably 'cause we're\Nenemies of the navy now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! I'll untie your ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.15,0:24:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta hurry! There has to be a\Nmap to the Grand Line in this base!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.55,0:24:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The ropes are tighter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:13.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.19,0:24:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.49,0:24:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Morgan vs. Luffy!\NWho's the Mysterious Pretty Girl?"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.83,0:24:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!
